  "description": "<i>International Hockey</i> is the sequel to Artworx's <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/slap-shot-hockey_\">SLAP-SHOT! Hockey</a>.<br><br>The game features standard single player vs computer (3 skill levels) and 2 player head-to-head modes. Controls offer precision passing, bone crushing body checks, with penalty shots and a shootout mode.  Make use of the walls on the arena to advance the puck. The player closest to the puck is under your control; others appear ghosted-out. Digitized speech, crowd noise and an organist add to the feel of the experience.",
